# Ecto migrations

When this rule applies, read and follow [`.cursor/skills/ecto-migrations/SKILL.md`](../skills/ecto-migrations/SKILL.md) **before** editing.

- **Uncommitted** migration: edit the file in place; do not add a follow-up migration to undo/redo the same change.
- After in-place edits: `MIX_ENV=test mix ecto.reset`, then `mix test`.
- **Committed or deployed**: add a new migration only; never rewrite old files.
